        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "feat: start onboarding for fresh CLI installs",
        "body": "## Summary\n- Route bare `openclaw` to classic onboarding when the active config is missing or has no authored settings, including empty and metadata-only configs.\n- Preserve Crestodian for configured installs and invalid existing configs that need repair.\n- Update Crestodian/onboard/TUI/testing docs plus the Crestodian first-run smoke expectation.\n\n## Verification\n- `git diff --check origin/main...HEAD`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/cli/run-main.exit.test.ts src/cli/run-main.test.ts`\n- `pnpm build`\n- `AUTOREVIEW_AUTO_TESTS=0 .agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode branch --base origin/main`\n- Fresh-state terminal proof with isolated temp `OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR`/`OPENCLAW_CONFIG_PATH`: bare `pnpm openclaw` reached `OpenClaw setup` before cancellation.\n\n## Real behavior proof\nBehavior addressed: Fresh bare `openclaw` now starts classic onboarding instead of Crestodian when the active config is missing, empty, or metadata-only; configured installs still open Crestodian, and invalid configs still avoid onboarding so repair remains reachable.\n\nReal environment tested: Local source checkout at `dae18659d42dcf2613990ca4895070bb94f63b1b`, Node `v24.14.0`, pnpm `11.1.0`, isolated temp OpenClaw state/config, interactive terminal driven by `expect`.\n\nExact steps or command run after this patch: `OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR=<tmp> OPENCLAW_CONFIG_PATH=<tmp>/openclaw.json expect ... spawn pnpm openclaw`, plus focused CLI tests and `pnpm build` listed above.\n\nEvidence after fix: Terminal output included `┌  OpenClaw setup`; `src/cli/run-main.exit.test.ts` now covers missing config, empty config, metadata-only config, non-TTY fresh automation guidance, and configured Crestodian routing.\n\nObserved result after fix: Bare `openclaw` reached the onboarding prompt for a fresh empty state; configured bare-root invocations remain on Crestodian in tests.\n\nWhat was not tested: Remote Blacksmith Testbox `pnpm check:changed` could not be started locally because `node scripts/crabbox-wrapper.mjs run --provider blacksmith-testbox ...` failed before provider allocation with no usable Crabbox binary (`../crabbox/bin/crabbox` absent and `crabbox`/`blacksmith` not on PATH). The Docker Crestodian first-run lane was not run locally.\n",
